OL,6,FA Northern Ireland sexual abuse
OL,7,Fcharity has announced that its free
OL,8,Fspecialist adult counselling service
OL,9,Fis to end on March 31.
OL,11,FNexus says it has been advised by the
OL,12,FDepartment of Health that there are no
OL,13,Fplans to replace the existing contract
OL,14,Ffor the service.
OL,16,FIn a statement, the charity said: "As
OL,17,Fof 29 February, the charity has
OL,18,Fstopped taking referrals, as the first
OL,19,Fmove to wind down the Department of
OL,20,FHealth-funded service.
