OL,6,FNexus CEO Joanne Barnes said "it is
OL,7,Fextremely disappointing that this
OL,8,Fspecialist service is coming to an end
OL,9,Fand that there is no direct
OL,10,Freplacement planned".JShe added: "For
OL,11,Fnow, our main focus is on continuing
OL,12,Fto support those who are already
OL,13,Freceiving counselling and ensuring
OL,14,Fthat they can complete their
OL,15,Ftherapeutic journey and recovery. We
OL,16,Fwant to stress that their service will
OL,17,Fnot be impacted.J"However, we are very
OL,18,Fconcerned for the 800 individuals
OL,19,Fcurrently on our waiting list who,
OL,20,Fregrettably, may not be able to
OL,21,Fbenefit from the specialist support
OL,22,Fthey require. "It's especially
OL,23,Fworrying when we know that many of our
OL,24,Fservice users will have waited until,
OL,25,Fwhat they felt was, the right time, to
OL,26,Ftake that initial brave step to seek
